Click on the "Application  -> Header [Is displayed == True] -> Objects Button "

Click on the "Dialog  -> Footer  -> Button [Has Text == True] AND [Text == OK]"

Double click on the "Application  -> Tree View [Is displayed == True] -> Tree View Item [Has Text == True] AND [Text == TDM365] -> Tree View Item [Has Text == True] AND [Text == xunit 02.09.2025 10:46:20 Автотестовый объект] -> Text "
